@sig (s: Severity) -> str
@source_file src/diagnostic/diagnostic.aria
@source_line 16
@purpose Converts Severity to its lowercase string name for rendering and severity comparison. Also used as a workaround for pattern matching on sum types — bag_add_diagnostic compares the string result rather than matching on the variant directly. [src: diagnostic.aria:163]

